  "reference_number": "CYB0007",
  "remarks": "\nYevgeniy Mikhaylovich SEREBRIAKOV is a member of GRU Unit 74455. In this capacity, Yevgeniy Mikhaylovich SEREBRIAKOV is or has been involved in relevant cyber activity through his leadership and oversight of GRU Unit 74455, in which SEREBRIAKOV is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting the commission, planning or preparation of relevant cyber activity. Such activity that Yevgeniy Mikhaylovich SEREBRIAKOV is or has been involved in undermines, or is intended to undermine, the integrity, propsperity or security of the United Kingdom or a country other than the United Kingdom.\n",
